# GIA DEEP Mind 2100

The sovereign‑grade AI core powering the Global Infrastructure Architecture (GIA) platform.  
This Worker exposes a secure JSON API that fronts your Deep Mind engine with strict trust‑zone enforcement and policy‑driven execution.

## Endpoint

`POST /`

Send JSON to interact with the AI core.

### Example Request

```bash
curl -X POST "https://<your-worker>.workers.dev" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "query": "System diagnostics",
    "trustZone": "internal"
  }'
